      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish the Program Reform Commission to review unnecessary Federal programs and make recommendations for termination, modification, or retention of such programs, and to express the sense of the Congress that the Congress should promptly consider legislation that would make the changes in law necessary to implement the recommendations.</title>
